about.summary: Deletes old files in Django Apps

name: django-cleanup
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "django-cleanup" %}
{% set version = "4.0.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "412c3f9417ddaaaa561b60237b109550b16e556db92d4616278fc7e1ad9ab0a4"

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: "python"
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - django

test:
  imports:
    - django_cleanup

about:
  home: "https://github.com/un1t/django-cleanup"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Deletes old files in Django Apps"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
